&lt;/center></description></item><item><title>数论提高</title><link>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E6%95%B0%E8%AE%BA%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98/</link><pubDate>Sun, 24 Jul 2022 15:39:05 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E6%95%B0%E8%AE%BA%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98/</guid><category domain="https://messywind.github.io/categories/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B/">算法竞赛</category><description>&lt;h2 id="前置数学符号介绍" class="heading-element">&lt;span>前置：数学符号介绍&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e7%bd%ae%e6%95%b0%e5%ad%a6%e7%ac%a6%e5%8f%b7%e4%bb%8b%e7%bb%8d" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>$\sum\limits_{i = 1} ^ {n}$：求和符号，例如 $\sum\limits_{i = 1} ^ {n}i = \dfrac{n \times (n + 1)}{2}$ 代表 $1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + \cdots + n$&lt;/li>
&lt;li>$\prod\limits_{i = 1} ^ {n}$：连乘符号，例如 $\prod\limits_{i = 1} ^ {n} i = n!$ 代表 $1 \times 2 \times 3 \times 4 \times \cdots \times n$&lt;/li>
&lt;li>$\lfloor \dfrac{x}{y} \rfloor$：向下取整符号，例如 $\lfloor \dfrac{5}{2} \rfloor = 2$&lt;/li>
&lt;li>$[]$：艾弗森括号，例如 $[n = 1]$ 只有 $n = 1$ 时才取值为 $1$&lt;/li>
&lt;li>$x \mid y$：整除符号，表示 $x$ 整除 $y$，也就是 $x$ 是 $y$ 的约数，例如 $2 \mid 4$&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="欧拉函数" class="heading-element">&lt;span>欧拉函数&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e6%ac%a7%e6%8b%89%e5%87%bd%e6%95%b0" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>定义：$\varphi(x)$ 为小于等于 $x$ 与 $x$ 互质的数，即
$$
\varphi(x) = \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {x} [\gcd(x, i) = 1]
$$&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>杜教筛</title><link>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E6%9D%9C%E6%95%99%E7%AD%9B/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Sep 2021 10:04:21 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E6%9D%9C%E6%95%99%E7%AD%9B/</guid><category domain="https://messywind.github.io/categories/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B/">算法竞赛</category><description>&lt;h2 id="杜教筛" class="heading-element">&lt;span>杜教筛&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e6%9d%9c%e6%95%99%e7%ad%9b" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>杜教筛可以在 $O(n ^{\frac{2}{3}})$ 的复杂度内求解积性函数的前缀和&lt;/p>
&lt;p>设数论函数 $f(x)$，求&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$\sum_{i=1}^{n}f(i)$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>令 $S(n) = \sum \limits_{i=1} ^{n} f(i)$，找一个数论函数 $g(x)$ 与 $f(x)$ 做卷积&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>狄利克雷卷积</title><link>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E7%8B%84%E5%88%A9%E5%85%8B%E9%9B%B7%E5%8D%B7%E7%A7%AF/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Sep 2021 21:05:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E7%8B%84%E5%88%A9%E5%85%8B%E9%9B%B7%E5%8D%B7%E7%A7%AF/</guid><category domain="https://messywind.github.io/categories/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B/">算法竞赛</category><description>&lt;h2 id="定义" class="heading-element">&lt;span>定义：&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%ae%9a%e4%b9%89" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>对于两个数论函数 $f(x),g(x)$ 那么它们的卷积 $h(x)$ 记作 $f(x) * g(x)$，式子如下：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$f(x) * g(x) = h(x) = \sum_{d \mid n} f(d)g(\frac{n}{d})$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>简记为 $h = f * g$&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="性质" class="heading-element">&lt;span>性质：&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e6%80%a7%e8%b4%a8" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;strong>交换律：&lt;/strong> $f * g = g * f$&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>BSGS、exBSGS</title><link>https://messywind.github.io/posts/bsgsexbsgs/</link><pubDate>Sun, 25 Jul 2021 13:42:18 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://messywind.github.io/posts/bsgsexbsgs/</guid><category domain="https://messywind.github.io/categories/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B/">算法竞赛</category><description>&lt;h2 id="textbsgs-baby-step-giant-step" class="heading-element">&lt;span>$\text{BSGS (Baby Step Giant Step)}:$&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#textbsgs-baby-step-giant-step" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>给定正整数 $a,b,p,a \perp p$ ，求满足&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$a^{x} \equiv b(\text{ mod } p)$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>的&lt;strong>最小非负整数&lt;/strong> $x$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>首先由欧拉定理的推论有：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$a^x\equiv a^{x\text{ mod }\varphi (p)}(\text{ mod }p)$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>所以 $a^x$ 在模 $p$ 意义下的最小循环节为 $\varphi(p)$ ，那么只需要考虑 $x \in [0,\varphi(p)-1]$ 即可，为了简便避免算欧拉函数，我们对欧拉函数进行放缩 $\varphi(p) \le p + 1$，那就是枚举 $x \in [0,p]$。那么我们对暴力枚举的算法做一个优化：令 $x =kt-y$ $,k=\lfloor \sqrt{p} \rfloor +1$，则原式为&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>